00:15:01,899 --> 00:15:04,200
Ayah sudah lama tidak kemari.

276
00:15:05,909 --> 00:15:07,340
Ayah mau bicara.

277
00:15:07,740 --> 00:15:08,909
Baik.

278
00:15:10,179 --> 00:15:11,450
Dae Ryook.

279
00:15:12,110 --> 00:15:14,720
Katamu kamu mau menikahi Nona Kim.

280
00:15:15,679 --> 00:15:16,950
Kamu sungguh-sungguh?

281
