292
00:15:46,250 --> 00:15:48,320
Seumur hidupmu dipertaruhkan.

293
00:15:48,320 --> 00:15:49,419
Ya.

294
00:15:49,549 --> 00:15:51,250
Aku yakin, Ayah.

295
00:15:52,649 --> 00:15:53,990
Aku pernah

296
