Terima kasih,

363
00:19:40,350 --> 00:19:41,620
Sekretaris Hong.

364
00:19:43,179 --> 00:19:45,820
Hai, silakan duduk di sana.

365
00:19:48,889 --> 00:19:51,330
- Ini.
- Terima kasih.

366
00:19:56,199 --> 00:19:57,300
Silakan.

367
00:20:00,729 --> 00:20:02,639
Mari bicara sambil minum kopi.

368
00:20:03,699 --> 00:20:05,409
- Silakan minum.
- Tentu.

